        previous = {'The Destiny Destroyers'},
        next = {'The Cardians\' Duty'},
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Kupipi in Heavens Tower for a cutscene.\n2. Speak to the 3 Tarutaru outside her office in the lobby area of Heavens Tower, and trade them the items they request:\n   - Sassa-Kotassa - Red Grass Cloth  - ( ➞ Materials ➞ Clothcraft)\n   - Sheelala - Yagudo Drink  - ( ➞ Food ➞ Meals ➞ Drinks)\n   - Habida-Jubida - Dream Fl. Petal  - ( ➞ Materials ➞ Alchemy 1)\n     - You can obtain this flower by killing Alraune in Bibiki Bay - Purgonorgo Isle after it has used the move Dream Flower. This Mission is not required to be active for the petal to drop.\n     - Drop the mob\'s HP to 20% and spamming Dia will speed up the process.\n3. Return to Kupipi for another cutscene. She will ask for a Wh. Rolanberry . (Alternatively, a Ri. Wh. Rolan.  will also work.)',
