        start_zone = 'The Boyahda Tree Map 1',
        start_pos = 'F-4',
        description = 'Mission Orders: You are destined for the Boyahda Tree in order to meet up with Jabbos once more. Magh Bihu is already en route. A friendly mandragora may be able to guide you to Magh Bihu\'s location if you give them a certain something.',
