        start_zone = nil,
        start_pos = 'K-8',
        description = 'Mission Orders: The black sword is a bit too inconvenient of a truth for some of the Yagudo. Reikuu has asked to find out more about a 5,000-year-old incident that the Yagudo have forgotten about. Seek out Incantrix once more.',
