        start_zone = 'Chateau d\'Oraguille',
        start_pos = nil,
        description = 'Mission Orders: Slackjawed Mukdrom\'s forces have captured a contingent of the Carmine Swallows. The victims have doubtless been taken to Fei\'Yin and require backup posthaste. Excenmille has chosen to examine the western half, so it falls to you to take the east side.',
