        repeatable = 'No',
        previous = {'Run, Excenmille, Run!'},
        next = {'Best Served Cold'},
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Zone into Fei\'Yin from Beaucedine Glacier for a cutscene.\n2. Obtain a Doll Gizmo.  You can buy them from the Auction House under Others ➞ Misc. 1.  It\'s also a 100% drop from the Manipulator in Temple of Uggalepih map 2 at (I-10)/(J-10) patrolling in the big room.\n   - Proto-Waypoint is the closest warp.\n   - The Unity Concord (Level 125) Warp is also a quick way to reach this NM. You will have to defeat the door guardian to get through the door to reach your target.\n   - The Manipulator respawns every 15 minutes.\n3. Trade the Doll Gizmo to the NPC Talos (H-7) map 2 in Fei\'Yin for a cutscene.\n   - This "NPC" is a pile of Doll Parts in front of a door when heading south down the hall (H-6) from the large room where Capricious Cassie spawns.\n   - The Talos for this mission does not show up on Wide Scan.\n   - The Talos will not be visible after completing the cutscene.\n   - If you are returning after grabbing the Doll Gizmo it is faster to use the Home Point #2 for the Cloister of Frost instead of navigating map 1 to exit A.\n4. After the cutscene, return to the Point of Interest next to Mirror Pond at (J-6) in Beaucedine Glacier for a cutscene.\n   - Subjob BLM and casting Escape puts you a short walk away from this position.\n5. Touch the Point of Interest again to begin a confrontation with Slackjawed Mukdrom (WAR)\n   - Has approximately 50k HP.\n   - Uses Mighty Strikes and has en-Drain on attacks.\n     - Can use Mighty Strikes multiple times.\n6. Touch the Point of Interest once more for a cutscene after defeating the Orc.\n7. Return to Chateau d\'Oraguille and click Door:Prince Royal\'s RM located at (H-7) for a final cutscene and your rewards.',
        notes = nil,
