        previous = {'The Gloom Phantom\'s Approach'},
        next = {'The Destiny Destroyers'},
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Gumbah in Bastok Mines HP #3 (J-7).\n   - From the Home Point #3, take the stairs mid-ways on the right, go up then bust a left, cross the bridge on your right and make an immediate right, open the door and Gumbah will be in the back room. This NPC is NOT sitting next to the Home Point, instead they\'re in the back room of a home.\n2. Speak to Brygid in Bastok Markets HP #4 (K-9) twice.\n3. After agreeing to assist her, Brygid will instruct you to select one of a list of NPCs to cosplay for her fashion show\'s contest.',
        notes = '1. If working multiple accounts simultaneously, any tradeable gear can be passed along to alts:\n   - Set and enable the lockstyle with the intended gear outside of The Steaming Sheep (will not persist through zone), trade the gear to the next character, repeat as needed.',
