        start_npc = 'Kohlo-Lakolo',
        start_zone = 'Port Windurst',
        start_pos = 'G-5',
        description = 'Mission Orders: Honoi-Gomoi is planning to parley with the Yagudo behind a magic tower in West Sarutabaruta. However, you have the egg that the Yagudo require. Disrupt their plans.',
