        start_npc = 'Andreine',
        start_zone = 'Celennia Memorial Library',
        start_pos = nil,
        description = 'Mission Orders: Skokkr Undrborn has taken possession of the Liber Daemonium. The tome holds the secrets for manifesting the Prime Weapons once more. Stygian ash, occasionally carried by pixies, is needed to serve as a suitable vessel. The item is quite rare, so head to Celennia Memorial Library and do some research to aid you.',
        reward = '[Key Item] Silver Knife membership card \nAbility to start Prime Weapons.',
        fame = nil,
        fame_level = nil,
        title = 'Searcher of the Voracious',
        repeatable = 'No',
        previous = {'Skokkr Undrborn\'s Temptation'},
        next = {'To Movalpolos!'},
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. (Optional) Speak to Andreine in the Celennia Memorial Library for a hint regarding Oshasha\'s whereabouts.\n2. Travel to Leafallia and interact with the Odyssean Passage for a cutscene.\n3. Trade a Stygian Ash to the Odyssean Passage for another cutscene. You will receive [Key Item] Bronze-hued tag.\n   - Stygian Ash drops from the Pixie family, which are easily found in Grauberg (S) around Witchfire Glen.\n     - The most accessible way to get to Witchfire Glen is using your Lightsworm on the blue sparkles near Batallia Downs Survival Guide. Once in Walk of Echoes, turn around and interact with the conflux just behind you to teleport to Witchfire Glen.\n     - Alternatively, either Campaign Warp to Grauberg or use the Survival Guide.\n     - Recall-Pashh will also bring you near the conflux in Pashhow Marshlands (S) which you may also use teleport to Witchfire Glen, but it requires you complete late game voidwatch quests.\n4. Travel to Outer Ra\'Kaznar (K-3), Upper Floor (map 1).\n   - To get here, it is easy to follow the marked path on the Outer Ra\'Kaznar page\'s maps.\n   - DO NOT interact with the roots at (J-3), continue over to (K-3) when you reach that spot. Otherwise you will be forced to take a teleport to the entrance and run through the entire area again.\n5. Interact with the Shrouded Workroom at (K-3) for a cutscene.\n   - Be careful, as there are Umbrils around the area.\n6. Return to Leafallia and interact with the Odyssean Passage for the final cutscene and your reward, completing the mission.\n7. Continue with the creation of your Prime Weapon by following the section below. You will need it to progress in the coming quests.',
        notes = '1. At this point, you can now open up access to two new Records of Eminence objectives. See the NPC Elijah in Upper Jeuno near Home Point #1 for more information.\n2. Caution:  you will need a Prime Weapon that can deal damage (not the shield or instrument) for future missions, so make sure to create one at some point.',
    },
