        start_pos = 'G-6',
        description = 'Mission Orders: Galka on their journey of rebirth are being targeted due to their knowledge of the Abyss. Gumbah and Oggbi have asked for your help in protecting the gates. Your first task is to head for Altepa Gate in the Western Altepa Desert and see what awaits you.',
